<SYNC Start=2174774><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2176150><P Class=KRCC>
건배
<SYNC Start=2177798><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2183124><P Class=KRCC>
